  "texts": [
    "The left side displays the VA, while the chat log on the right shows the VA's messages in white speech bubbles and the user's in green.",
    "We input the user's statement, \"I always end up quitting diary writing after just three days.",
    "I want to do something about that,\" using voice and supplemented missing elements through dialogue with a VA. As a result of the dialogue, 6W1H needs and a new service were extracted, as shown in Figs.",
    "10 and 11, respectively.",
    "Since no specific person was designated, the who and whom elements were left blank, and as it is a new service, the is_released element was set to 0."
  ],
